videos.headline: LSU connects on deep ball to set up field goal
videos.description: Joe Burrow ups the tempo and lofts a great ball to Terrace Marshall Jr. for the 38-yard gain.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (LSU connects on deep ball to set up field goal) 2019/09/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Texas' Ingram drops wide-open pass in end zone
videos.description: The Longhorns go for it on 4th-and-goal and look like they have a touchdown, but Keaontay Ingram drops the ball with no LSU defender near him.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Texas’ Ingram drops wide-open pass in end zone) 2019/09/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: LSU stuffs Texas on 4th-and-goal again
videos.description: Texas comes away with zero points in the red zone for the second straight possession as Sam Ehlinger gets stood up by the LSU defense.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (LSU stuffs texas on 4th and goal again) 2019/09/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ehlinger links up with Eagles for 55-yard Texas TD
videos.description: LSU's Kristian Fulton tries to jump the route, but mistimes his jump leaving Brennan Eagles open for the 55-yard Texas score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ehlinger links up with Eagles for 55-yard Texas TD) 2019/09/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Burrow threads needle on TD to Jefferson
videos.description: Joe Burrow throws it in a tight space to Justin Jefferson for the six-yard score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Burrow threads needle on TD to Jefferson) 2019/09/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Burrow and Jefferson strike again for LSU before halftime
videos.description: Justin Jefferson rises to catch Joe Burrow's pass for the difficult touchdown grab before the half for LSU.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Burrow and Jefferson strike again for LSU before halftime) 2019/09/07

videos.headline: Ehlinger caps off 19-play drive with rushing TD
videos.description: Sam Ehlinger calls his own number and runs up the gut for a two-yard score to trim LSU's lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ehlinger caps off 19-play drive with rushing TD) 2019/09/07

videos.headline: Ehlinger's pass is on the money to Smith for a Texas TD
videos.description: Sam Ehlinger somehow fits the ball in to his receiver Jake Smith for a 20-yard score to cut into the Longhorns' deficit.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ehlinger's pass is on the money to Smith for a Texas TD) 2019/09/07

videos.headline: Burrow increases LSU's lead with his 3rd TD strike
videos.description: Joe Burrow sees Terrace Marshall Jr. in one-on-one coverage and fires a 26-yard touchdown pass to extend the Tigers' lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Burrow increases LSU's lead with his 3rd TD strike) 2019/09/07

videos.headline: Duvernay bursts through LSU defense for Texas TD
videos.description: Sam Ehlinger throws a quick pass to Devin Duvernay and the Texas wideout splits a couple LSU defenders and goes 44 yards for the score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Duvernay bursts through LSU defense for Texas TD) 2019/09/07

videos.headline: Edwards-Helaire sprints outside for LSU touchdown
videos.description: LSU goes back up two possessions after Clyde Edwards-Helaire bounces outside and gets in the end zone for a 12-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Edwards-Helaire sprints outside for LSU touchdown) 2019/09/07

videos.headline: Burrow and Jefferson deliver knockout punch for LSU
videos.description: Joe Burrow completes a pass to Justin Jefferson on third-and-17, and the receiver goes 61 yards for his third touchdown of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Burrow and Jefferson deliver knockout punch for LSU) 2019/09/07

videos.headline: Burrow's big day leads LSU by Texas
videos.description: Joe Burrow tosses four touchdown passes, including two in the fourth quarter, as LSU wins in Austin 45-38.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Burrow’s big day leads LSU by Texas) 2019/09/07 ESHEET SOTFULL
